    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In a devastated world, sisters who have returned from the depths of despair grow the sustenance they need to live today...</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893980/extras/36f9671cb07ff205f09970e358ad5ddf.avif?t=1686884600\" width=480 height=270 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Flow</h2>One day passes with each slide, and a new object appears.<br>The three types of objects that appear are dirt, sisters, and zombies at random.<br>Bombs can make the objects disappear, and by this way zombies can be defeated.<br>The number of food will increase when vegetables are harvested by continuing to mix soil, and the population will increase with the number of food.<br>The number of days of survival when the population reaches 0 is the game's play score.<br><br>Survive and defeat the looming threat and countless zombies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Easy to Use Slide Puzzle!<br></li><li>Evolution By Merging the Same Image!<br></li><li>Harvest the Vegetables You've Grown!<br></li><li>If A Sister Appears, You Have A Chance!<br></li><li>Zombies Eat other Objects.<br></li><li>Zombies Blow Up With Bombs!<br></li><li>Fever Can Occur Depending On the Conditions...!<br></li><li>Simple, But Endless Fun!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893980/extras/340fecee75c95141f96f8eda51866971.avif?t=1686884600\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Survive by making full use of bombs. However, the rate of zombies increases with each zombie rush.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893980/extras/549c3acaadb7de1a8abb716725556a06.avif?t=1686884600\" width=480 height=270 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Graphic</h2>Survive in a post-apocalyptic world with cute characters and adorable vegetables!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893980/extras/ec88a852c2f103b58e0d9c8d1f4e72cf.avif?t=1686884600\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893980/extras/afbef22fc46d083d6049a19d01407529.avif?t=1686884600\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893980/extras/dda08c11eb4212e83525a937fc1ea688.avif?t=1686884600\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893980/extras/12a8c2702c344b801aaefef57266f825.avif?t=1686884600\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
